    "reasoning": "The segment analysis uses FY2025 revenue and operating income by segment, product-line growth drivers from MD&A, and management's Q2 FY2026 commentary on Copilot, Azure, Foundry, Fabric, gaming, search, and Windows. The conclusion follows from which segments generated the largest growth and profit dollars and which areas management identified as strategically central or under pressure."
